  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You use Twisted Chakra to generate a multitude of chakra arms, claws, mouths, and other offensive appendages that assault all creatures in the selected area. All creatures of your choice in range when you cast this Vermilion Art or who begin their turn in the area must succeed a Dexterity saving throw, taking <strong>8d12 Necrotic Damage</strong> on a failed save, or half as much on a successful save.</p><p>At the start of your turn, you may move the target area this affects up to <strong>60 feet</strong> to another location.</p><p><strong>Tier X:</strong> You can magnify your Vermilion Art beyond its base power. By increasing its Twisted Chakra cost by 5, you increase the tier of this Art by 1. If you do, increase the size of the cube by <strong>10 feet</strong> and its damage by <strong>3d12</strong> per tier.</p>",
